OL,3,CJunior doctors get three-month
OL,4,Cextension to strike mandate
OL,6,FJunior doctors have secured a three-
OL,7,Fmonth extension to their strike
OL,8,Fmandate.
OL,10,FIt's part of their negotiations with
OL,11,Fthe Welsh Government over pay.
OL,13,FBMA Cymru Wales has confirmed junior
OL,14,Fdoctors in Wales would now have the
OL,15,Fright to enact industrial action over
OL,16,Ftheir pay until 17 September 2024
OL,17,Finstead of 17 June 2024, when the
OL,18,Fmandate was due to run out.
