OL,3,CJunior doctors get three-month
OL,4,Cextension to strike mandate
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government and NHS employers
OL,7,Fhave agreed to the extension to allow
OL,8,Ftalks to continue, with a view to end
OL,9,Fthe pay dispute.
OL,11,FThe BMA union says the change is down
OL,12,Fto "recognising the strength of
OL,13,Ffeeling amongst junior doctors" after
OL,14,F98% voted for a walkout back in
OL,15,FDecember, from a turnout of 65%.
OL,17,FCo-chairs of the Welsh Junior Doctor
OL,18,FCommittee Dr Oba Babs-Osibodu and Dr
OL,19,FPeter Fahey said they were "pleased"
OL,20,Fwith this development.
