OL,3,CJunior doctors get three-month
OL,4,Cextension to strike mandate
OL,6,FThey said: "Whilst we hope to put an
OL,7,Fend to our pay dispute through pay
OL,8,Fnegotiations by reaching a credible
OL,9,Fdeal and restoring our pay, it was
OL,10,Fimportant to secure more time for our
OL,11,Fmandate.
OL,13,F"The extension allows us to focus on
OL,14,Ftalks but also provides us with the
OL,15,Fscope to get organised and enact our
OL,16,Flegal right to strike should we need
OL,17,Fto. This is about honouring the
OL,18,Femphatic mandate of our members.
