OL,3,CJunior doctors get three-month
OL,4,Cextension to strike mandate
OL,6,F"Doctors have experienced real terms
OL,7,Fpay cut of almost a third since 2008.
OL,8,FThey voted overwhelmingly to put an
OL,9,Fend to the devaluing of their service,
OL,10,Fthey know they are not worth a third
OL,11,Fless than their predecessors and they
OL,12,Fknow the time is now to stick up for
OL,13,Fthe profession and turn the tide of
OL,14,Fthe continued erosion of their pay
OL,15,Fonce and for all".
OL,17,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,18,F"We recognise the strength of feeling
OL,19,Famong BMA members and that industrial
OL,20,Faction is never taken lightly.
