OL,3,CJunior doctors get three-month
OL,4,Cextension to strike mandate
OL,6,F"This is a government that listens and
OL,7,Fengages to find solutions and we are
OL,8,Fcommitted to working in social
OL,9,Fpartnership with the BMA and NHS
OL,10,Femployers to ending the current junior
OL,11,Fdoctor, consultant and SAS doctor
OL,12,Fdisputes.
OL,14,F"Employers extending the strike
OL,15,Fmandate and unions suspending the
OL,16,Findustrial action both build trust in
OL,17,Fthat partnership. We won't be
OL,18,Fproviding a running commentary while
OL,19,Fnegotiations take place."
