OL,3,CJunior doctors get three-month
OL,4,Cextension to strike mandate
OL,6,FLast month, BMA Cymru Wales announced
OL,7,Fit was suspending forthcoming
OL,8,Findustrial action for Consultants and
OL,9,FSAS doctors and pausing announcing
OL,10,Fmore strike dates for junior doctors
OL,11,Fto allow pay negotiations to take
OL,12,Fplace.
OL,14,FAs part of their disputes, junior
OL,15,Fdoctors have taken part in 10 days of
OL,16,Findustrial action since January this
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,19,FThe UK Government has previously said
OL,20,Fthat Wales has received a record level
OL,21,Fof funding this year.
